  <div class="mx:px-[112px] md:px-[64px] py-64px xs:px-16px flex flex-col  gap-[64px]">
    <TextSection title="Knowledge, Unchained">
      The Independent Society of Knowledge is a movement, through which, an alternative route to scientific inquiry is
      established. It is a community driven organization that seeks a new wave in academia by solving its problems and
      offering new ideas.
    </TextSection>
    <div class="grid xs:grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-32px">
      <TextSection title="Solutions" mode="vertical" class="w-full">
        Our solutions empower researchers with state-of-the-art resources, from computational packages to
        collaborative
        environments.
      </TextSection>
